Tonight I was delighted to learn a bit more of science history, learning about some of the many contributions we had previously left behind in the textbooks

https://t.co/2FzXUIHady

When I was little, I aspired to be an archaeologist.

That’s why today, as a #SoftwareEngineer, I appreciate putting together word docs, manually setting configs & sending tons of email, just to deploy to prod.

So I can experience the past in first person.
